---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about The ReUse Market — a Boise, Idaho 501(c)(3) nonprofit that has been keeping reusable art and craft materials out of landfills since 2006."
>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-14 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d4a2d 0%, #3d6b3d 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <nav class="text-sm text-green-300 mb-4" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-green-100">About Us</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white">About Us</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-green-100 text-lg max-w-xl">Redirecting scrap materials for creative reuse since 2006.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 md:py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Body text -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The goal of the ReUse Market is to keep clean, reusable art and craft materials out of the landfill — and put them into the hands of artists, crafters, teachers, and others who can repurpose them into imaginative works of art and useful personal or household items.
          </p>

          <p>
            The ReUse Market is entirely operated through the efforts of community-conscious volunteers and donors. With your generous and ongoing support, the ReUse Market can continue its mission to serve our creative and environmentally aware community.
          </p>

          <h2>What is the ReUse Market?</h2>
          <p>
            The ReUse Market is a Boise, Idaho nonprofit <strong>501(c)(3)</strong> organization. We collect clean, reusable art and craft materials that might otherwise end up in a landfill, and make them available to teachers, artists, crafters, and the general public for creative reuse. All donations are tax-deductible.
          </p>

          <h2>How did it start?</h2>
          <p>
            The ReUse Market began in 2006 with Tracy Cochran, who found that in her interior design business, lots of unique sample materials were getting thrown away. She believed those materials could be put to good use if they could reach artists, students, crafters, and other creative-minded individuals. She was right.
          </p>
          <p>
            After five years, Tracy passed the reins in Fall 2011 to the staff of Kieffer Design Group in downtown Boise, Idaho.
          </p>
          <p>
            In 2014, the ReUse Market was temporarily closed while an advisory board searched for a new location and additional volunteers. In February 2015, the ReUse Market co-located with North End Organic Nursery at 3777 W. Chinden Blvd. in Garden City, ID — where it remains today.
          </p>

          <h2>We Need You!</h2>
          <p>
            The board is always seeking volunteers and additional board members to guide the market toward future success. Our primary needs are:
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>Identifying volunteers to expand and maintain Market operations</li>
            <li>Finding donors, grants, and sponsorship to support the retail space</li>
            <li>Connecting with artists and like-minded community organizations</li>
          </ol>
          <p>
            If you're interested in becoming part of this mission or have resources to donate, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> with your information and ideas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/volunteer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold text-white transition-colors" style="background-color: #d97706;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#b45309'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#d97706'">
            Volunteer With Us
          </a>
          <a href="/donate" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors border-2" style="border-color: #5a8a5a; color: #5a8a5a;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#5a8a5a'; this.style.color='white';" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'; this.style.color='#5a8a5a';">
            Make a Donation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside>
        <div class="rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 reveal" style="background-color: #f2f7f2; border: 1px solid #e8f0e8;">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-4" style="color: #2d4a2d;">Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>Founded in <strong>2006</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>Boise, Idaho <strong>501(c)(3)</strong> nonprofit</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>Entirely <strong>volunteer-operated</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>Located in <strong>Garden City, ID</strong></span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5 text-green-600">✓</span>
              <span>All donations <strong>tax-deductible</strong></span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl p-6 reveal reveal-delay-1" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fde68a;">
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg mb-3" style="color: #92400e;">Visit Us</h3>
          <address class="text-sm text-amber-900 not-italic leading-relaxed">
            3777 W Chinden Blvd.<br />
            Garden City, ID 83714<br />
            <span class="text-amber-700 text-xs">(upstairs in North End Organic Nursery)</span>
          </address>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-amber-900">
            <strong>Thu – Sat</strong>, Noon to 5 p.m.
          </p>
          <a href="/hours" class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold underline" style="color: #92400e;">
            Check hours calendar →
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
